網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=67f4e968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=ed440784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"069ec8be36dceb2e18327ba1681e20ab43aa4c7e","tid":1077761,"uid":205226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b3bd391d9a116cea1366bcb8d7fc561426102df","tid":1077761,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170b5a875232069fe5c329fbe61b0ad6610467c7","tid":1077761,"uid":205226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8833109480f6a7ff4c9d3aeca666eab69af8185","tid":1077761,"uid":31132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:01:22.000Z","msg":"排公立有排 <br />\n你不如去左私家睇一睇  最貴應該2000蚊到<br />\n食下血清素會唔會訓得番先"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生哥。唔敢畀屋企知，私家好貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"其實訓唔到覺真係會搞到抑鬱，真係人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打可以照去排公家先啦，坊間好似有d資助睇私家架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"越瞓唔到越煩，越煩越瞓唔到，之後再諗d唔開心嘅嘢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d01a300d6b493b100d4bfbcf90b633010dbed0","tid":1077761,"uid":205226,"like":0,"dislike